                "url": "https://pressgazette.co.uk/media-audience-and-business-data/media_metrics/biggest-local-news-websites-uk-2023/",
                "version": 1
              },
              {
                "detail": 0,
                "format": 0,
                "mode": "normal",
                "style": "",
                "text": ". Plenty of negative numbers on growth – is there a consistent pattern among the ones growing, though?",
                "type": "text",
